Inventory storage model. Sample storage for list of missing objects in a SSCC:

  • inventoryNumber: urn:epcglobal:cbv:bt:pi:mions_200912041545_mixte
  • epcClass: urn:epc:id:sgtin:318757.0802072
  • objectUri: urn:epc:id:sscc:318757.000000187578
  • epcList: (urn:epc:id:sgtin:318757.0802072.2009101512371, ...)
  • expectedEpcList: (urn:epc:id:sgtin:318757.0802072.2009101512371, ...)
  • totalProductRead: 6
  • totalProductExpected: 8
